<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      header {
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      header h1 {
        color: white;
      }
      .container {
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 80%;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        color: #fff;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background: purple;
      }
      .content {
        margin-top: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .content p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #777;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: #4caf50;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Learning Management System</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="header">Reset Your Password</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Dear <b><%= userName %></b>,</p>

          <p>
            We received a request to reset your password for your Learning
            Management System account.
          </p>

          <p>
            Please click the button below to reset your password. If you did not
            request a password reset, you can ignore this email, and your
            password will remain unchanged.
          </p>

          <a href="<%= redirectUrl %>" target="_blank" class="button"
            >Reset Password</a
          >

          <p>
            For security reasons, the link will expire in 15 minutes. If the
            link has expired, you can request a new one by visiting our website
            and following the password reset instructions.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you have any questions or encounter any issues, feel free to
            contact our support team. We're here to help you!
          </p>

          <p>Thank you, and stay secure!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
          <p>
            If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:[Support Email]">www.mohdshahid303@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
          <p class="highlight">
            Thank you for using our Learning Management System!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
